 * Open a connection to an S/FTP site identified by the
 * profile name.
 * 
 * @param cmdline A command line of the form: <br>
 *                <br>
 *                [+Q] profile-name
 *                <br>
 *                <br>
 *                where: <br>
 *                +Q Quiet. Do not display any warnings or errors.
 * 
 * @return 0 on success, non-zero on failure.
